No. I'm your husband.

1147
01:46:30,625 --> 01:46:32,250
- Yan.
- Yes.

1148
01:46:35,000 --> 01:46:38,041
No. Don't get close yet.

1149
01:46:38,125 --> 01:46:39,875
This must be the boss.

1150
01:46:39,958 --> 01:46:41,416
No, you'll get possessed, Lin.

1151
01:46:41,500 --> 01:46:43,291
