1193
01:51:23,833 --> 01:51:26,708
- We're both victims of this jerk.
- Papa, wake up.

1194
01:51:29,458 --> 01:51:30,625
Papa.

1195
01:51:30,708 --> 01:51:33,791
- Ario is cruel.
- Wake up, Pa.

1196
01:51:33,875 --> 01:51:36,833
Ario is cruel.

1197
01:51:38,333 --> 01:51:39,958
Ario is cruel.

1198
01:51:41,791 --> 01:51:43,833
Papa…

1199
