- Rafa.
- Jefri.

1220
01:54:24,500 --> 01:54:26,500
Rafa.

1221
01:54:26,583 --> 01:54:30,416
- Rafa.
- Rafa must be short for Rafatar.

1222
01:54:30,500 --> 01:54:31,958
